CDemu Virtual CD/DVD emulator

yay gcdemu

to resolve missing xhci_pci firmware
$ lsmod | grep xhci_pci
xhci_pci               20480  0
xhci_pci_renesas       20480  1 xhci_pci
xhci_hcd              286720  1 xhci_pci

lspci | grep -i renesas
if renesas:
yay -S upd72020x-fw
